{"tid":2087913,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] 如何用國安法批鬥屋企藍絲","createTime":"2020-07-01T02:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T02:39:35.000Z","uid":133966,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3956ad634c0cbdc2cdbd8c742245055c8297d72a","tid":2087913,"uid":133966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"假設藍絲廢老係你屋企睇緊TVB<br />\n而咁好彩你係用Smart TV, <br />\n姐係手機有得控制你屋企電視, e.g. Samsung嘅Smartview<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3S9YSo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3S9YSo.png&h=83c66e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁你就可以將個電視換做你個手機嘅畫面<br />\n<br />\n又或者只少個Smart TV可以轉台去睇Youtube<br />\n然後用YouTube播以下歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uZV3hvz4IXQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuZV3hvz4IXQ&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=2d52df01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uZV3hvz4IXQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fyVzHJUu9h8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfyVzHJUu9h8&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=ea5f7bc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fyVzHJUu9h8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SYnIBxLsPAQ&amp;list=PLyXRKgUCRx6Xs4rH2R1_PqoB_k6g4o-ul\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSYnIBxLsPAQ%26list%3DPLyXRKgUCRx6Xs4rH2R1_PqoB_k6g4o-ul&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=60565b0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SYnIBxLsPAQ&amp;list=PLyXRKgUCRx6Xs4rH2R1_PqoB_k6g4o-ul</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有更好嘅紅歌, 歡迎留係下面comment<br />\n如果你屋企廢老熄左部電視<br />\n你就話要報警, 因為懷疑屋企廢老唔尊重國家唔尊重黨<br />\n危害國家安全<br />\n<br />\n之後只會有兩個可能, <br />\n1) 佢開番電視播紅歌<br />\n2) 佢繼續同你嘈<br />\n<br />\n(1) 你可以番入房打機做番自己做開嘅野, 佢就繼續聽紅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(2) 你就真係報警, 順便分薄警力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後廢老不滿你做任何紅野, 都可以推到去國安法<br />\n<br />\n一字記之曰: 煩, 要令到藍絲廢老覺得煩但又吹你唔脹<br />\n<br />\n祝手足批鬥路上順風順水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d7a1f8253f51bb5d4244344f350a2d23d83a9e","tid":2087913,"uid":133966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:05:48.000Z","msg":"甚至同廢老講, <br />\n依家唔播番4個鐘紅歌<br />\n會比人拉嫁"},{"pid":"585deda642021671c8faabbbf3b6e2b971e0ee13","tid":2087913,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d153497277edcb2139937ba0ed9a401dae480e","tid":2087913,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:08:16.000Z","msg":"批鬥埋你隔離屋唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日夜播紅歌邊個報警就邊個唔愛國<br />\n班狗上到黎都要跟住一齊唱<br />\n唔唱就違反公務員效忠政府呢個條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起都開心呀屌你老母閪"},{"pid":"38ba3d84261d305491e2e4bcfe6148f99cec974e","tid":2087913,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ce161bf60ba0513f387d012696d615dd7c7a4b","tid":2087913,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:10:23.000Z","msg":"幫隔離屋部電視轉埋台"},{"pid":"65e019096dc80de46efc942e13662e63e7373abd","tid":2087913,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e95ac3d1fdf13d9f882782d18f1b1651b5e636","tid":2087913,"uid":133966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88ce161bf60ba0513f387d012696d615dd7c7a4b","tid":2087913,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:10:23.000Z","msg":"幫隔離屋部電視轉埋台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"好似要用緊同一個wifi先得<br />\n除非佢wifi冇password就....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe39d1d3b9b8f58cdf18f09e48df560010387344","tid":2087913,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:22:06.000Z","msg":"戇鳩鳩，有時間做啲實際嘅嘢好過啦"},{"pid":"d067d7755f7e86182208675d78a41c303f33495a","tid":2087913,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:28:49.000Z","msg":"一早同屋但個歌個講咗<br />\n叫佢地學識唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n唔識唱到時批鬥死佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a883c6f4098584d2598de6292aa157bbe0a3271","tid":2087913,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:39:35.000Z","msg":"國安法過撚左， 直接舉報佢分裂國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}